  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180°C.",
    "Slice the malted bread into quarters and place on a baking sheet.",
    "Top each bread quarter with a slice of cheddar cheese and a sprinkle of malted British cheese.",
    "Bake in the oven for 5 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Meanwhile, slice the spring onions and apple.",
    "Arrange the sliced pears on a serving platter.",
    "Top the pears with the baked bread quarters and sprinkle with sliced spring onions.",
    "Drizzle with softened butter and serve immediately."
